{
  "info": {
    "name": "Internet Stability Tracker API v3",
    "description": "Complete API collection for Internet Stability Tracker v3 — advanced network monitoring with AI insights, security auditing, and real-time diagnostics.\n\n## Live Production URL\nAll requests default to the **live deployment**:\n```\nhttps://backend-cold-butterfly-9535.fly.dev/api\n```\n\n## Switch to local dev\nChange the `base_url` collection variable to `http://localhost:8000/api`.\n\n## Swagger UI\n- **Production**: https://backend-cold-butterfly-9535.fly.dev/docs\n- **Local**: http://localhost:8000/docs\n\n## WebSocket\n```\nwss://backend-cold-butterfly-9535.fly.dev/api/ws/live\n```\n\n## Authentication\nAll per-device endpoints require `X-Client-ID` header (UUID). The frontend auto-generates and persists this in localStorage.\n\n## Rate limits\n| Endpoint | Limit |\n|----------|-------|\n| `POST /test-now` | 5 req / 60 s per IP + X-Client-ID |\n| `POST /reports` | 5 req / 60 s per IP + X-Client-ID |\n| `DELETE /measurements` | 3 req / 60 s (admin key required) |\n| `GET /my-connection` | 10 req / 60 s per IP |\n| All others | 60 req / 60 s per IP |\n\n## New in v3\n- Gaming metrics with grade + game recommendations\n- Video call quality predictor (Zoom, Teams, Meet)\n- Router health check & reboot detection\n- Activity recommendations (What Can I Do?)\n- Is It Just Me? global outage checker\n- Advanced diagnostics: packet loss, jitter, bufferbloat, MTU, DNS leak, VPN speed\n- Network security audit (port scan, privacy score, intrusion detection)\n- Historical visualization (heatmap, distribution, percentiles, correlation, timeline)\n- AI insights enhanced + natural language assistant\n- ML predictions (next hour, outage probability, best download time)\n- Smart alerts (Telegram, Discord, SMS)\n- User preferences (theme, layout, metrics)",
    "version": "3.2.0",
    "_postman_id": "ist-api-v3",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "https://backend-cold-butterfly-9535.fly.dev/api",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Production URL. Change to http://localhost:8000/api for local dev."
    },
    {
      "key": "client_id",
      "value": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Device UUID — update to match your browser's stored X-Client-ID"
    },
    {
      "key": "report_id",
      "value": "1",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "ID of a community report — update after creating one"
    },
    {
      "key": "webhook_id",
      "value": "1",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "ID of a registered webhook — update after calling POST /webhooks"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/../health" },
            "description": "Returns service status, UTC timestamp, and environment."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Healthy",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\"status\":\"healthy\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-12T00:00:00Z\",\"environment\":\"production\"}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Speed Test",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Run speed test now",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "X-Client-ID", "value": "{{client_id}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/test-now" },
            "description": "Triggers an immediate speed test. Rate limited: 5 req/60s."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "My Connection info",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "X-Client-ID", "value": "{{client_id}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/my-connection" },
            "description": "Returns public IP, ISP, ASN, org, country, region, city, lat/lon, and last speed test."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Measurements",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List measurements",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "X-Client-ID", "value": "{{client_id}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/measurements?skip=0&limit=50",
              "query": [
                { "key": "skip", "value": "0" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "50" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Recent measurements",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "X-Client-ID", "value": "{{client_id}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/measurements/recent?hours=24",
              "query": [{ "key": "hours", "value": "24" }]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete all measurements (admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              { "key": "X-Admin-Key", "value": "your-admin-key-here" },
              { "key": "X-Client-ID", "value": "{{client_id}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/measurements" },
            "description": "Requires admin API key. Rate limited: 3 req/60s."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
